If build fails you most probably don't have Allegro 5 installed.
This project expects Allegro 5 static libraries in /usr/local/lib and Allegro 5 headers in /usr/local/include

To install do this:

svn checkout https://alleg.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/alleg/allegro/branches/5.0 allegro
cd allegro
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DSHARED=off ..
make
sudo make install

